sun.jvm.hotspot.debugger.cdbg

Interface EnumType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IntType, Type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicEnumType

    public interface EnumType
extends IntType
    Describes enumerated types. Enumerations are like ints except that they have a set of named values.
